        "text": "B-3 Let S be a finite set of points in the plane. A linear partition of Sis an unordered pair {A, B} of subsets of S such that AUB = S, AnB = D, and A and B lie on opposite sides of some straight line disjoint from S (A or B may be empty). Let Ls be the number of linear partitions of S. For each positive integer n, find the maximum of Ls over all sets S of n points.",
